    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_40E4D630-222E-0135-BE6F-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can move quiz questions or groups after you've created them. You can manually drag and drop the question or group, or you can use the Move option, which is also accessible for keyboard users. </p>
<p>You can also reorder questions within a question group. However, please note that quiz ordering inside a question group is only a quiz management tool for instructors. Your students will always see questions from a group in a random order.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: To help identify quiz questions in the Move dialog menu, make sure each quiz question or group has a specific name.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_quizzes" data-step-uuid="2e133003-840e-4f5c-bd61-1b95428dedc6">
    <h2 id="open_quizzes" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Quizzes</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/758/638/original/07bf436d-ea99-4f4e-9440-578c30109e34.png" srcset="" alt="Open Quizzes" height="241" width="156">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_40E50CC0-222E-0135-BE71-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Quizzes</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="add-classic-quiz" data-step-uuid="562e1d02-122b-45e6-958d-138984bd2887">
    <h3 id="add-classic-quiz" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Quiz Engine</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/787/591/original/20421b0e-42ab-4b32-b60a-d9c9582a9248.png" srcset="" alt="Select Quiz Engine" height="531" width="484">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8fbd71f1-5a45-4e9e-b0c3-30e08bbce694" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If your course has New Quizzes enabled, you must select a quiz engine.</p>
<p>To select New Quizzes, click the <strong>New Quizzes</strong> option [1].</p>
<p>To create a classic quiz, click the <strong>Classic Quizzes</strong> option [2].</p>
<p>Then click the <strong>Submit</strong> button [3].</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Learn more about <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-a-quiz-using-New-Quizzes/ta-p/1173" target="_blank">creating a quiz using New Quizzes</a>.<a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-a-quiz-using-New-Quizzes/ta-p/1173" target="_blank">?</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit_quiz" data-step-uuid="791e14de-aff6-4faf-972a-847f73f5f6e1">
    <h2 id="edit_quiz" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Quiz</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/250/822/original/0729e691-16af-4734-8c84-5757786f3e72.png" srcset="" alt="Edit Quiz" height="329" width="750">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_40E54380-222E-0135-BE73-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the quiz you want to edit. Click the quiz <strong>Options</strong> icon [1], then click the <strong>Edit </strong>link [2]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_questions" data-step-uuid="da15cd9e-35c4-4025-87c6-764f3e3d4e62">
