      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="reorder_with_move_option" data-step-uuid="2b201625-1e57-4d8a-a131-e760d7e9ddbc">
    <h2 id="reorder_with_move_option" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Reorder with Move Option</h2>
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_40E7A5E0-222E-0135-BE7F-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have a large quiz, you may want to use the Move option to reorder your quiz.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
